===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to be [[greedy]]
#: {{zh-x|做人 不要 這麼 貪心。|Don't be so '''greedy''' in life.}}
# to be [[fond]] of; to have an [[insatiable]] [[desire]] for
#: {{zh-x|貪玩|to be '''preoccupied with''' having fun}}
#: {{zh-x|貪睡|to be a lover of sleep}}
# to [[pursue]] something (excessively or inappropriately)
#: {{zh-x|貪便宜|to be anxious to get things on the cheap}}
#: {{zh-x|唔好 貪 快 衝紅燈 過 馬路 啊{aa3}！||C}}
# to [[embezzle]]
#: {{zh-x|貪官|'''corrupt''' official}}
#: {{zh-x|貪 了 幾 千 萬|to have '''embezzled''' several hundred million}}

